{"id": "1228242364079013948", "channel_id": "1228242364079013948", "type": 0, "author_id": "1195661471053516821", "author_name": "qwer_s", "author_bot": false, "content": "新活动“我们的过错”这一关，要求六十级，这是在直接拒绝萌新玩了吗？关卡小怪都是多段攻击，每段都是上百。本来一局就需要打很久，每次活动又不给复现，重复打你那个鬼关卡有什么意义？难道说策划组是有什么折磨玩家的恶趣味？😅", "timestamp": "2024-04-12T07:16:39.236000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1228242364397522995", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-04-12-15-07-50-433_com.qookkagames.z1.gp.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 91439, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1228242364079013948/1228242364397522995/Screenshot_2024-04-12-15-07-50-433_com.qookkagames.z1.gp.hk.jpg?ex=6a00d997&is=69ff8817&hm=ddec12c029176a1f028759701b43b326eb5abbfd0c8652b9b02e5a2a43d47b40&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1228242364079013948", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」新活动难度问题", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1228317392858517516", "channel_id": "1228317392858517516", "type": 0, "author_id": "1079677800023347250", "author_name": "juzi6912", "author_bot": false, "content": "從初入遊戲到現在，美術和文案的表現一直在線，這次神父還新加入了新的融蝕怪物，覺得這次的新美術也很好看，想誇誇👍\n這個雨傘男和變異的索非亞真的很有感覺！背景血月的視覺表達也在線！\n文案也很不錯，成功引出了提燈教會的「伊芙」，並且在整個劇情上面居然還非常的連貫！👏\n真的，有這樣的美術和文案非常需要大誇特誇！🛐\n而且！神父的打擊感提升了！感謝製作團隊！🍟\n請問有沒有把這些背景做成首頁背景板的計畫呢，非常好看！\n而且真的很期待喚醒體皮膚如果實裝上線會是什麼樣子😍買爆！\n最後誰能解答一下神父的白布眼罩經歷了什麼變成了黑鐵眼罩呢？是不是我錯過了哪些內容🧠", "timestamp": "2024-04-12T12:14:47.491000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 7}], "attachments": [{"id": "1228317393562894346", "filename": "4bfa3e9f5a1949ebc0cfed4a14ff9992.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 61285, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1228317392858517516/1228317393562894346/4bfa3e9f5a1949ebc0cfed4a14ff9992.png?ex=6a0076b7&is=69ff2537&hm=8be8d6acb4cb45463831133abb27ea5e551cb9e5f61b60c5e04cf2c7af3e24bb&"}, {"id": "1228317393898569763", "filename": "c91ae0790d9bd52e2b7359e1cb547913.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 113159, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1228317392858517516/1228317393898569763/c91ae0790d9bd52e2b7359e1cb547913.png?ex=6a0076b7&is=69ff2537&hm=3a82cd03f11efc4cf5184d8205aa2c767e13b0cd53ff0190391dc9f06a3d961e&"}, {"id": "1228317394179723286", "filename": "2d9f0d959c0dd7d08de878eca1177be1.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 663934, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1228317392858517516/1228317394179723286/2d9f0d959c0dd7d08de878eca1177be1.png?ex=6a0076b7&is=69ff2537&hm=93c78f0cc03017420ee288447b14e4774b0666ad93799d5aba074500a09fbb7b&"}, {"id": "1228317394598887424", "filename": "ae3ff7c373beab15e0770e78b61bfed2.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1271625, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1228317392858517516/1228317394598887424/ae3ff7c373beab15e0770e78b61bfed2.png?ex=6a0076b7&is=69ff2537&hm=495374e45b54c211e90019c20560727f84ac